# Git Workflow — Yael

When handling any Git request in this project, follow `.cursor/skills/git-agent/SKILL.md`.

## Quick Reference

- **Branch**: `yael-dev` (never `main` or `rachel-dev` for daily work)
- **Push target**: `git push origin yael-dev`
- **origin** = `yael88761-svg/calorie-counter-app-backend` (Yael's fork)
- **upstream** = `rachelf-dev/calorie-counter-app-backend` (team repo — fetch/merge only)
- **Teammate**: Rachel on `rachel-dev`; merge to `main` together via PR
- **Never commit**: `node_modules/`, `.env`, secrets
- **Commit only when user explicitly asks**
